      },
      "date": "2012-05-28 20:32:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nOne question I had was why did this not cause any test failures?  Was there some other symptom that made this defect visible that should have been checked for?\n\nI would have thought that this would prevent the filesystem from being unmounted, or similar?",
