      "date": "2012-05-28 21:29:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d09c578c-a909-11e1-a81e-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
