      "date": "2012-05-28 21:48:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/36713418-a90c-11e1-a81e-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
